This application shows the cumulative count of COVID-19 cases in Louisiana by parish by day. Click the time icon in the upper right of the next screen to see the change in cumulative counts over time. 

Click the up arrow at the bottom of the next screen to see the underlying data. Click the options button of the table to export the data.

Please note that these data will be updated daily at noon.

Click OK to continue.
